msgstr ":menuselection:`属性编辑器 --> 渲染 --> 色彩管理`"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:101
msgid "Render settings for color management."
msgstr "色彩管理渲染设置。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:105
msgid "Display"
msgstr "显示"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:117
msgid "Display Device"
msgstr "显示设备"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:108
msgid "The device that the image is being viewed on."
msgstr "正在查看的图像的设备。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:110
msgid ""
"Most computer monitors are configured for the sRGB color space, and so when working on a computer usually this option should just be left to the default. It would "
"typically be changed when viewing the image on another display device connected to the computer, or when writing out image files intended to be displayed on another "
"device."
msgstr ""
"大多数计算机显示器都配置为sRGB色彩空间，因此在计算机上工作时，通常应将此选项保留为默认值。当在连接到计算机的另一个显示设备上查看图像时，或者当写出要在另一个设备上显示"
"的图像文件时，通常会改变它。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:115
msgid "Rec709 is commonly used for HDTVs, while XYZ and DCI-P3 are common for digital projectors."
msgstr "Rec709通常用于高清电视，而XYZ和DCI-P3通常用于数字投影仪。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:117
msgid "Color management can be disabled by setting the device to None."
msgstr "通过将设备设置为无，可以禁用颜色管理。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:120
msgid "Render"
msgstr "渲染"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:138
msgid "View"
msgstr "视图"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:123
msgid "These are different ways to view the image on the same display device."
msgstr "这些是在同一显示设备上查看图像的不同方式。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:127
msgid "Standard"
msgstr "标准"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:126
msgid ""
"Does no extra conversion besides the conversion for the display device. Often used for non-photorealistic results or video editing where a specific look is already "
"baked into the input video."
msgstr "除了显示设备的转换之外，没有额外的转换。通常用于非照片级真实结果或视频编辑，其中特定外观已经烘焙到输入视频中。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:130
msgid "Filmic"
msgstr "电影"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:130
msgid ""
"For photorealistic results and better handling of high dynamic range colors. The contrast can be adjusted by changing the *Look* option for the Filmic view transform."
msgstr "用于逼真的结果和更好地处理高动态范围的颜色。可以通过更改电影视图变换的Look选项来调整对比度。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:133
msgid "Filmic Log"
msgstr "电影日志"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:133
msgid ""
"Converts to Filmic log color space. This can be used for export to color grading applications, or to inspect the image by flattening out very dark and light areas."
msgstr "转换为电影日志色彩空间。这可用于导出到颜色分级应用程序，或通过展平非常黑暗和明亮的区域来检查图像。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:136
msgid "Raw"
msgstr "Raw"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:136
msgid "Intended for inspecting the image but not for final export. Raw gives the image without any color space conversion."
msgstr "用于检查图像，但不用于最终输出。Raw在没有任何色彩空间转换的情况下提供图像。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:138
msgid "False Color"
msgstr "假色彩"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:139
msgid "Shows a heat map of image intensities, to visualize the dynamic range."
msgstr "显示图像强度的热图，以显示动态范围。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:141
msgid "Exposure"
msgstr "曝光"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:141
msgid ""
"Used to control the image brightness (in stops) applied before color space conversion. It is calculated as follows: :math:`output\\_value = render\\_value × "
"2^{(exposure)}`"
msgstr "用于控制在色彩空间转换之前应用的图像亮度(停止)。计算方法为: :math:`output\\_value = render\\_value × 2^{(exposure)}`"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:145
msgid "Gamma"
msgstr "伽玛"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:144
msgid ""
"Extra gamma correction applied after color space conversion. Note that the default display transforms already perform the appropriate conversion, so this mainly acts "
"as an additional effect for artistic tweaks."
msgstr "在色彩空间转换后应用额外的伽马校正。请注意，默认显示变换已经执行了适当的转换，因此这主要作为艺术调整的附加效果。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:148
msgid "Look"
msgstr "效果"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:148
msgid "Choose an artistic effect from a set of measured film response data which roughly emulates the look of certain film types. Applied before color space conversion."
msgstr "从一组测量的胶片响应数据中选择艺术效果，这些数据大致模拟某些胶片类型的外观。在色彩空间转换之前应用。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:153
msgid "Use Curves"
msgstr "使用曲线"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:151
msgid "Adjust RGB Curves to control image colors before color space conversion. Read more about using the :ref:`ui-curve-widget`."
msgstr "调整RGB曲线以在色彩空间转换之前控制图像颜色。阅读有关使用 :ref:`ui-curve-widget` 小组件的更多信息。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:156
msgid "Sequencer"
msgstr "序列编辑器"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:162 ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:181
msgid "Color Space"
msgstr "色彩空间"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:159
msgid ""
"The color space that the Sequencer operates in. By default, the Sequencer operates in sRGB space, but it can also be set to work in Linear space like the Compositing "
"nodes, or another color space. Different color spaces will give different results for color correction, crossfades, and other operations."
msgstr ""
"序列器操作的色彩空间。默认情况下，序列器在sRGB空间中运行，但也可以设置为在线性空间中工作，如合成节点或其他色彩空间。不同的色彩空间将为颜色校正，交叉渐变和其他操作提供"
"不同的结果。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:165
msgid "Image Files"
msgstr "图像文件"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:167
msgid ""
"When working with image files, the default color space is usually the right one. If this is not the case, the color space of the image file can be configured in the "
"image settings. A common situation where manual changes are needed is when working with or baking normal maps or displacement maps, for example. Such maps do not "
"actually store colors, just data encoded as colors. Those images should be marked as *Non-Color Data*."
msgstr ""
"使用图像文件时，默认色彩空间通常是正确的色彩空间。如果不是这种情况，可以在图像设置中配置图像文件的色彩空间。例如，需要手动更改的常见情况是使用或烘焙法线贴图或置换贴"
"图。这样的地图实际上不存储颜色，只是编码为颜色的数据。这些图像应标记为非彩色数据。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:173
msgid ""
"Image data-blocks will always store float buffers in memory in the scene linear color space, while a byte buffer in memory and files in a drive are stored in the "
"color space specified with this setting:"
msgstr "图像数据块将始终将浮动缓冲区存储在场景线性色彩空间的内存中，而内存中的字节缓冲区和驱动器中的文件存储在使用此设置指定的色彩空间中："

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:177
msgid ""
"The color space of the image file on a drive. This depends on the file format, for example, PNG or JPEG images are often stored in sRGB, while OpenEXR images are "
"stored in a linear color space. Some images such as normal, bump or stencil maps do not strictly contain 'colors', and on such values, no color space conversion "
"should ever be applied. For such images, the color space should be set to *None*."
msgstr ""
"驱动器上图像文件的色彩空间。这取决于文件格式，例如，PNG或JPEG图像通常存储在sRGB中，而OpenEXR图像存储在线性色彩空间中。某些图像(例如法线，凹凸或模板贴图)不严格包含“颜"
"色”，并且在此类值上，不应应用任何色彩空间转换。对于此类图像，色彩空间应设置为“ 无”。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:183
msgid ""
"By default only renders are displayed and saved with the render view transformations applied. These are the Render Result and Viewer image data-blocks, and the files "
"saved directly to a drive with the Render Animation operator. However, when loading a render saved to an intermediate OpenEXR file, Blender cannot detect "
"automatically that this is a render (it could be e.g. an image texture or displacement map). We need to specify that this is a render and that we want the "
"transformations applied, with these two settings:"
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，仅显示渲染并使用应用渲染视图转换保存渲染。这些是渲染结果和查看器图像数据块，以及使用“渲染动画”操作符直接保存到驱动器的文件。但是，当加载保存到中间OpenEXR文"
"件的渲染时，Blender无法自动检测到这是渲染(它可能是例如图像纹理或置换贴图)。我们需要指定这是一个渲染，并且我们希望应用这两个设置的变换："

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:193
msgid "View as Render"
msgstr "预览渲染结果"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:193
msgid ""
"Display the image data-block (not only renders) with view transform, exposure, gamma, RGB curves applied. Useful for viewing rendered frames in linear OpenEXR files "
"the same as when rendering them directly."
msgstr "使用视图变换，曝光，伽马，RGB曲线显示图像数据块(不仅仅是渲染)。用于查看线性OpenEXR文件中的渲染帧与直接渲染时相同。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:198
msgid "Save as Render"
msgstr "另存为渲染图"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:196
msgid ""
"Option in the image save operator to apply the view transform, exposure, gamma, RGB curves. This is useful for saving linear OpenEXR to e.g. PNG or JPEG files in "
"display space."
msgstr "图像保存操作符中的选项可应用视图变换，曝光，伽玛，RGB曲线。这对于将线性OpenEXR保存为显示空间中的PNG或JPEG文件非常有用。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:201
msgid "OpenColorIO Configuration"
msgstr "OpenColorIO配置"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:203
msgid ""
"Blender comes with a standard OpenColorIO configuration that contains a number of useful display devices and view transforms. The reference linear :term:`color space` "
"used is the linear color space with Rec. 709 chromaticities and D65 white point."
msgstr "Blender附带标准的OpenColorIO配置，其中包含许多有用的显示设备和视图转换。使用的参考线性色彩空间是具有Rec的线性 :term:`色彩空间` 。709色度和D65白点。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:208
msgid ""
"However, OpenColorIO was also designed to give a consistent user experience across `multiple applications <http://opencolorio.org/CompatibleSoftware.html>`__, and for "
"this, a single shared configuration file can be used. Blender will use the standard OCIO environment variable to read an OpenColorIO configuration other than the "
"default Blender one. More information about how to set up such a workflow can be found on the `OpenColorIO website <http://opencolorio.org/>`__."
msgstr ""
"但是，OpenColorIO还旨在为 `多个应用程序 <http://opencolorio.org/CompatibleSoftware.html>`__,提供一致的用户体验 ，为此，可以使用单个共享配置文件。Blender将使用标准OCIO"
"环境变量来读取除默认Blender之外的OpenColorIO配置。有关如何设置此类工作流的更多信息，请访问 `OpenColorIO网站 <http://opencolorio.org/>`__。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:215
msgid "Blender currently use the following color space rules:"
msgstr "Blender目前使用以下色彩空间规则："

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:217
msgid "``scene_linear``"
msgstr "``scene_linear``"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:218
msgid "Color space used for rendering, compositing, and storing all float precision images in memory."
msgstr "用于在内存中渲染，合成和存储所有浮点精度图像的色彩空间。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:219
msgid "``data``"
msgstr "``data``"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:220
msgid "Color space for non-color data."
msgstr "非颜色数据的色彩空间。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:222
msgid "``XYZ``"
msgstr "``XYZ``"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:222
msgid "Standard linear XYZ color space. Used for effects such as blackbody emission to convert from physical units to the *scene_linear* color space."
msgstr "标准线性XYZ色彩空间。用于将黑体发射等效果从物理单位转换为 *scene_linear* 色彩空间。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:226
msgid "``color_picking``"
msgstr "``color_picking``"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:225
msgid ""
"Defines the distribution of colors in color pickers. It is expected to be approximately perceptually linear, have the same gamut as the *scene_linear* color space, "
"map 0..1 values to 0..1 values in the scene linear color space for predictable editing of material albedos."
msgstr "定义颜色选择器中的颜色分布。预期它在近似上是线性的，具有与场景线性色彩空间相同的色域，在场景线性色彩空间中将0..1值映射到0..1值，以便可预测地编辑材料反照率。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:228
msgid "``default_sequencer``"
msgstr "``default_sequencer``"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:229
msgid "Default color space for the Sequencer, *scene_linear* if not specified."
msgstr "序列编辑中使用默认的色彩显示空间。如未指定，则为 *scene_linear*。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:230
msgid "``default_byte``"
msgstr "``default_byte``"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:231
msgid "Default color space for byte precision images and files, *texture_paint* if not specified."
msgstr "字节精度图像和文件的默认色彩空间，如果未指定，则为 *texture_paint*。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:233
msgid "``default_float``"
msgstr "``default_float``"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:233
msgid "Default color space for float precision images and files, *scene_linear* if not specified."
msgstr "浮点精度图像和文件的默认色彩空间，如未指定，则为 *scene_linear*。"

#: ../../manual/render/color_management.rst:235
msgid ""
"The standard Blender configuration includes support for saving and loading images in `ACES <https://www.oscars.org/science-technology/sci-tech-projects/aces>`__ "
"(`code and documentation <https://github.com/ampas/aces-dev>`__) color spaces. However, the ACES gamut is larger than the Rec. 709 gamut, so for best results, an ACES "
"specific configuration file should be used. OpenColorIO provides an `ACES configuration <http://opencolorio.org/configurations/index.html>`__ file, though it may need "
